scripts.vercel-build1: yum install gcc-c++ cairo-devel pango-devel libjpeg-turbo-devel giflib-devel
scripts.vercel-build2: yum install libuuid-devel libmount-devel && cp /lib64/{libuuid,libmount,libblkid}.so.1 node_modules/canvas/build/Release/
scripts.vercel-build: yum install libuuid-devel libmount-devel zlib && cp /lib64/{libuuid,libmount,libblkid,libz}.so.1 node_modules/canvas/build/Release/ && pnpm run build
